| 1 | Background color theme | #0B0F1A dark navy | #FFFBF5 warm cream | #FFFFFF pure white | Yes |
| 2 | Shadow style | Glow (0 0 20px with primary color) | Soft warm (rgba dark, 0.04-0.08) | None (no shadows anywhere) | Yes |
| 3 | Border treatment | Transparent rgba(255,255,255,0.08) | Warm tone #F0E7DB solid | Hairline 0.5px #F3F4F6 | Yes |
| 4 | Corner radius | 12-16px (rounded-xl) | 16-20px + pill (rounded-2xl/full) | 0-6px max (rounded-md) | Yes |
| 5 | Typography weight | 600-700 bold, tight tracking | 500-600 semibold, open tracking | 300-400 light, editorial scale | Yes |
| 6 | Status color expression | Neon glow badges (colored glow shadow) | Pastel pills (colored bg + saturated text) | Dot-only + text weight (6px dot) | Yes |
| 7 | Sidebar theme | Pure dark #080C14 + gradient accent | Warm dark purple #1A1625 + coral accent | Light #F8FAFC + 3px primary left border | Yes |

